     SHORT="nss_ldap is a library for using ldap for name service"
      LONG="
nss_ldap is an RFC 2307-compliant set of C library extensions which
allows X.500 and LDAP directory servers to be used as a primary source
of aliases, ethers, groups, hosts, networks, protocol, users, RPCs,
services and shadow passwords (instead of or in addition to using flat
files or NIS).
"
